data.description: Thoughtfully planned home sitting on 2.5 acres in the Eagles Watch Subdivision. This home is located only 3.4 miles from the Stagecoach entrance and Stagecoach Lake. This extensive property offers privacy and plenty of space for outdoor activities. Outdoor living space is maximized with two covered front porches and a fenced-in yard that includes multiple patio areas. Extending from the fenced yard, the property expands a couple of acres into an Aspen tree forest and borders the Stagecoach Ski Mountain property. As you enter the home you will see a living area complete with a pellet stove, as well as an open dining and kitchen area. In addition to the primary living space, the home offers a spacious bonus living room above the garage. The home has 3 bedrooms and 3.5 bathrooms, including a main floor master bedroom with an ensuite bath and its own patio area that is hot tub ready! As you make your way upstairs, you will find two more bedrooms, a full bathroom and a bonus room that could be utilized as a play room, office or anything else you may need. This home is a must see for anyone looking to have a beautiful outdoor space with a cozy, private home.
